NAME

printfile - print file

SYNOPSIS

printfile [-sq codebook_coder] file

OPTIONS

-sq codebook_coder
String. Name of the codebook coder to use for the printing of SID-format files.

DESCRIPTION

printfile prints the contents of file to stdout. printfile determines the file type of file from its magic number.

The -sq option gives the name of the codebook-coder file (a SQ-format file) to use in the printing of a SID-format file. If file is SID format, this option is required.

SEE ALSO

QccPack(3)
